Dialogue.A25128C5449F84A547AA8C925296FBBF_06FC410: For, like, the next few weeks, or... this month, or...
Dialogue.BF0825FC429B686CFA31E59E7B24A5F8_47CFF90: Four minutes, you can do this!
Dialogue.3F44E5C64155DF62A37CF98A76710F74_861A10F: Get ready for enemies over here!
Dialogue.98566695457541A9DFB831907B8C204C_97A9259: Ghost Boss Bonus Objective: Eliminate more husks!
Dialogue.F955756341B3BBE09E4B408ACC59D45A_97A9259: Ghost Boss survival is comin' at ya.
Dialogue.8D3B1329444576B3358BCCA668F41788_C2C5A2E: Good dusk to you. It is I, Madcap. Unjustly deposed king of the rotlands in the pine bog between exits 7b and 7c.
Dialogue.90D968DE47637459B16CD988E0942805_97A9259: Good job! All bonus objectives complete!
Dialogue.BD23A145416FD70BBD0B17AF8F3CBB28_06FC410: Good news, all three SEE-bots confirmed a weakness to BluGlo.
Dialogue.B6EE74C246ECDBF8C4E73BB2B7A709FC_B222EAD: Got some bad news for you. All ghosts are bad.
Dialogue.6AE4EEF645C31C9C02F71D89FC332244_47CFF90: Great work, you've got more waves to come so heal up and repair.
Dialogue.342B92044DEE10D88C695CB2DA7A2B87_47CFF90: Great work, you've got more waves to come so, uh, heal up and repair.
Dialogue.9671F82E47E398DEF3AABFB6E5BB0040_06FC410: Gross. What is that? I hate it.
Dialogue.9AEE5D694587C56A91BA79BFA53E0DC8_C2C5A2E: Hah. It is worse than disgusting! It is repellant! Revolting! Where is your coating of slime?
Dialogue.8F535FE94DAF7D8B0188BDBB78C5915B_06FC410: He was always putting his name on everything he made.
Dialogue.9A7C9C0548D96366D81780B014794C70_06FC410: He's at seventy five percent health!
Dialogue.5BF9983A40DCD5B04F2D509BF686C1B6_06FC410: He's at twenty five percent health!
Dialogue.2507B4AE41566F6874626793F27502C6_06FC410: He's back together... and I guess now we just wait...
Dialogue.5FE14E964183A3B642D9D08FF88D6D16_C2C5A2E: Health, please! Where is a page when one needs one?
Dialogue.5554D9E6400FA5D9503156A3CA4B0A8F_C2C5A2E: Health? Yeah, I could use some.
Dialogue.87B5E4664FA702C63949349CFF77C0E0_861A10F: Here we go. "Rumors of Ghost Activity."
Dialogue.13CC68AC43F70BF1A3A10DA1AC296DC2_861A10F: Here's a little somethin somethin for ya.
Dialogue.C7B839754DD5979701D8FEA521034865_97A9259: Hey, Commander. Is endless presents a scam?
Dialogue.BC3E0D034428F4BF2E3A12AC3733667B_06FC410: Hey, Doc... it feels silly trying to talk to you.
Dialogue.213C331B4E64AD8312FD988F60EE2A7E_861A10F: Hey, I was thinkin' of you
Dialogue.BD6DE16241786AB61C56AEB273FE3217_06FC410: Hey, PIRA-SEE-Bot. Look at Keelhaul and Blakebeard. What do you see?
Dialogue.C0FB18F7424C445DD66A56B09F12B96D_861A10F: Hey, smasher! This is my fort!
Dialogue.A81DDDDF465083C29AC6A1A19E0887FE_FB122F8: Hit the X with your pickaxe.
Dialogue.6E260D0D445485D32E02798CD8FE5128_C2C5A2E: Hmm. I do find you disgusting...
Dialogue.7FA8F2BC48E8AF22EF0A0AB356A2CF7E_97A9259: Hoho, you're good! Another package protected!
Dialogue.373AB9F14E8A0DC2AB35569BBC22B39B_FB122F8: Husks are on the way. Build those defenses.
Dialogue.C87683FC49947EE4077AFA86D469C483_72190CE: I DIED. You can find a stamp.
Dialogue.80ED7B554F69B7D9520F3C8969CD088F_C2C5A2E: I accept. I will rally behind Jilly, and you will become my first subject.
Dialogue.5A3926F7444288F96E0389A21B897C45_C2C5A2E: I am in need of health, friend.
Dialogue.40C2E68D4A921E5EAA13DC960207C51A_C2C5A2E: I am in need of health, good citizen.
Dialogue.8C8E772D46ADE4D8758BADB62108D506_C2C5A2E: I am in need of health.
Dialogue.A1A024404C7B22462BC6798F6F4DE3C1_47CFF90: I believe we have a momentary reprieve from the waves of husks.
Dialogue.3EF715D84A05897D92193E8F66BB2C14_0ADEFA4: I can't believe it! You're the best.
Dialogue.48E34BE643314774F2C5658665EEC872_72190CE: I do have one note. I'm not hearing any lamentations.
Dialogue.F476AA3E4B781F9F1DF208A749E1C74D_861A10F: I don't care for that one.
Dialogue.C34BD8BC42E6EEC62D1DB399CAFA0006_47CFF90: I don't know what's better. Natural disasters fighting...
Dialogue.F84F5D7F45D20D82DCCCF192718FD406_AB3C42C: I don't think they'll be happening this year...
Dialogue.DFC2337542F8959E4BA802BA60B143B1_97A9259: I feel like my soul just got a brain freeze.
Dialogue.953D4BD04F070DCA5ED15B90C9E9636B_C2C5A2E: I have a domed cap and a woody stem that turns light blue when bruised.
Dialogue.8AA2C6D24B61860492DA648432E582B0_47CFF90: I have no idea how you people live like this on a daily basis.
Dialogue.19A6243D4EC4FCBD99E72585C5B3A0F1_C2C5A2E: I have settled on my demand.
Dialogue.A263F6294945CEB4320A6BA795112B0A_0ADEFA4: I know it's a lot to ask.
Dialogue.7F534CBC42E9C0275AB97B924D1290FB_C2C5A2E: I lack the context to understand what my loyal subject was doing, but I note with pride that he was doing it with gusto.
Dialogue.F26242304210D1FB4E30A9A8027C2E1D_06FC410: I meant to say that earlier.
Dialogue.C27DA9374969FE0D2F3FBEB2ACA0F9F5_AB3C42C: I never really watched the show. Not my thing.
Dialogue.B9FB802441B6DBADB189CDB4C082876F_47CFF90: I normally would not feel the need to say that, but Dennis has taught me that nothing should ever be assumed.
Dialogue.81DB32D646671B81956C3D80DB044DE2_72190CE: I reacted a bit strongly earlier. There is nothing wrong with larping.
Dialogue.35411A5E47F58C6F5391239D01B72339_0ADEFA4: I really can't leave without it.
Dialogue.6BDDB23B4ED16EB6138888A8E1C22CDF_AB3C42C: I searched the area for plans, but... nothing.
Dialogue.D565C89B485DA386CE946AAB62808799_47CFF90: I suggest bridging the gaps on the island.
Dialogue.9E98F0374C1DA400CC7D2EAA95E3DEDB_47CFF90: I suggest not falling into that lava.
Dialogue.8EBA4C8B441284BE6C13EEAC2AC34076_47CFF90: I suggest using this time to build up your defenses!
Dialogue.2CA0C7194E298E77CA2CC3B7B349AD7D_CC240C1: I think Willow's afraid of this room, too.
Dialogue.64051BC94E7A3CEE09BD559E2270BA58_06FC410: I think one box might do it.
Dialogue.A42F789345811A910F2FC2AF2F0355D9_06FC410: I think today we learned that... nobody really has it together.
Dialogue.83C138984AE898287A304393C361067A_06FC410: I think we're looking at a blockbuster here.
Dialogue.2BE2B8264F6DEA3566602888FFDEE9BA_06FC410: I think you'd be proud of us.
Dialogue.6F0507B244E913F9E7F6E4A297C2DC8A_06FC410: I want everything to shine like the deflector shields of the VSS Gallant!
Dialogue.848715BE4830DE8E024FF5B2869A6D54_06FC410: I was able to recover data from Pop's last hour...
Dialogue.C20F067C4143B62C12FFD3A4570BDB19_06FC410: I was being sarcastic. We're not doing that.
Dialogue.2F0AD3014505E7FBA8B6789F21103629_C2C5A2E: I will have my enemies driven before me.
Dialogue.800A9FE548332C1E81F7FEA40DCC4645_06FC410: I wish Desiree was here to see it...
Dialogue.B1CA6D244172D9E77C0D57925CA8B58A_06FC410: I wish you could see how far we've taken your work.
Dialogue.D764BF3A4532404743A95BBBCA6F1730_C2C5A2E: I would have my kingdom restored.
Dialogue.89AC5FCC45AE831B638074A406B4E4EA_47CFF90: I would never encourage reckless combat behavior...
Dialogue.2642077B417B72F68E8D94B72129F0DD_47CFF90: I wouldn't trust any other team with a mission this difficult. Stay focused and you'll make it.
Dialogue.CF97665246316C856E2870BE3BEC7CF9_97A9259: I'd call that like... the smallest possible win condition.
Dialogue.623D2591485D06297E14AE80632BB081_06FC410: I'll go see if anyone's interested...
Dialogue.B0F088D34946F47A7155A78EA928CF3D_861A10F: I'll have to watch my goods around you.
Dialogue.FA4D04014AFB885FEB436DBCAB68A8C9_06FC410: I'm getting hits for Pop everywhere. It's almost like -
Dialogue.E70F0AFE46D84C3CB08741BC3FF54B79_CC240C1: I'm sorry if this is rude to ask, but...
Dialogue.7D01B25D464DEA6708007E869703D357_AB3C42C: I'm surprised so many of the props survived.
Dialogue.B321A4724B4530E51B0F99BBBC90863B_0ADEFA4: I'm trapped and under attack! This is so unfair!
Dialogue.85AF23F8416BF5D08F20DAB0E9FF8B3E_72190CE: I'm working a few angles here. There's gonna be some overlap.
Dialogue.C138A9B5401410BE28967193745DAE83_47CFF90: I've added a little illumination to guide your efforts.
Dialogue.EE61B84F454F41BA16F9D3AB9A787F51_861A10F: I've never set eyes on a bigger V.
Dialogue.E113143F4C62A7D6799450B82D045F90_C2C5A2E: I- I- I was once a king. One day I shall rule again.
Dialogue.7B1026864F8D7F4B77AD4C986C36269D_C2C5A2E: If ammo had fumes, I'd be runnin' on 'em.
Dialogue.DF3C08064C5F4AB93F4FF7999940D495_7D086D9: If it isn't we won't really have time to regret it so... sure.
Dialogue.CF470AB8473A057875FBA39DE523D42B_47CFF90: If one base falls, the next drop will have fewer supplies.
Dialogue.5D4AF81A42F27626C229DEA2556F33F2_47CFF90: If things get hectic, don't forget to look for the light.
Dialogue.4DA3DE8042F1F277DEC5C4B11D8B5765_06FC410: If we build it quickly, there might be a bonus for you.
Dialogue.9286C9C448C4C844A9EE76B4D82EA3F7_06FC410: If we can find a way to blu-ier, glow-ier, deadlier BluGlo.
Dialogue.35E572A54BCED05792E7C7935C0E77E2_97A9259: If we don't protect any of the presents, Christmas is of course ruined.
Dialogue.E953D6DD4028D301032DB8B8CA33DCD6_47CFF90: If we don't push them back, this whole base is going to come down.
Dialogue.505368E84EED7F674F2904A52B1431ED_B222EAD: If you don't have a buddy, the ghosts'll get ya for sure.
Dialogue.C1A75A8E4FBD7B56C7311CBF9CADC6E5_47CFF90: In the meantime, perhaps we should try again.
Dialogue.C10BD5CE4383405D3B8F0D93FC513431_861A10F: Is that how you treat your friends?
Dialogue.8151E9D14039014B27F04CB26502D509_06FC410: Is that the set? The actual set for Beyond the Stellar Horizon?
Dialogue.3676E64E447F5EC940F58CB8FF6F0613_06FC410: Is that your shadow quadsponder from episode 210?
Dialogue.E0B60B8944E38D5750CF86BC0C87FC2C_72190CE: Is this really the time for sarcasm? I died.
Dialogue.1EA767474D9514FD9B43A0B765BCB345_47CFF90: It is almost time for extraction!
Dialogue.F70BFA3541C4535956F43FA6E05A15D3_C2C5A2E: It is as sweet as the sound of a dead frog mouldering in the damp leaves.
Dialogue.DD2BE23E44E9C36911940681DA550708_C2C5A2E: It means that now you will rise and walk, a knight of my kingdom.
Dialogue.2040A2A04A05563646DA2BB8241A9B07_97A9259: It seems too good to be true.
Dialogue.5B3B32134AE40CD2D452FBA1AD7FDE85_EAAE146: It takes ten seconds to fill out the card.
Dialogue.D1D7A7D44CD31E821637618B15FFC2FE_FB122F8: It's a simple concept, really. You defend the target, and there are cannons.
Dialogue.E253855C4A4A2EC26C51AC9D4A9FB016_06FC410: It's getting too dangerous. I have to pull you out now!
Dialogue.C3A425B042DD40467219F7A373102601_06FC410: It's got great lower back support. Nice swivel.
Dialogue.FB0F5C904CCA24668FAA4E916773CE7E_861A10F: It's got nothin' to do with fightin' husks.
Dialogue.4CE1A84B48248D455B6FA19376F6A30B_AB3C42C: It's in rough shape but I think we can make it work.
Dialogue.DBB70C61429C763F7B20B5B06F4BDDF4_861A10F: Just dealing a bit of death.
Dialogue.05FEBED941B4402806D79EA942832AE1_72190CE: Just keep it open. What else have you got goin' on?
Dialogue.B0307D864CABA2E3B2C63CBB92A3E36A_97A9259: Just spitballing here, but maybe we should protect the sensor.
Dialogue.70FCA9554B189296D35C7BB6BEE01199_72190CE: Keels, can you believe this? She wants to do a verbal RSVP. No, thank you.
Dialogue.B9AA73074ECBE99F7FD267821062A774_06FC410: Let me do some research from here... until then it might be best to stay away.
Dialogue.1431C72E41B3BBF58CA39BA8793C95AE_06FC410: Let's add the mast and some rigging.
Dialogue.B7E39D1E4F7A1879E4D6F99EFBCACD3B_47CFF90: Let's get back in the fight!
Dialogue.8AE12538481BECF98EE8B89163D91996_06FC410: Let's go back and start building.
Dialogue.8237A77F4DE29B5A395CC98A1D993FC0_97A9259: Let's see what those ghost sensors sensed. I'm thinking... ghosts.
Dialogue.328F8C4B4FB338F43076FE9B7F06C7F3_06FC410: Let's... let's keep it anyway. Just in case.
Dialogue.94ECAA3E419043944D12FC8D34F92E73_861A10F: Lok, could you tell your imaginary friend that she's a little scary?
Dialogue.E796C4D340C97E4A253C26BD713F475E_C2C5A2E: Look sharp! Those flingers fling husks!
Dialogue.29FCC79140EF71D007B7D7AFC070D029_06FC410: Looks like a bad storm is in the forecast. I need to pull you out before it gets there. You have 2 days.
Dialogue.6864DD15474A1588344BD9BCE2CB7220_47CFF90: Make sure you're communicating with your team.
Dialogue.8ADD92214EE2574E8324A58366C983AE_06FC410: Maybe he just saw the rift, and coincidentally terminated all communications... while screaming.
Dialogue.876C3F0740A2684962AF8898730599DC_97A9259: My gut and/or memory tell me that when something lands in the world, husks go wild.
Dialogue.1FC4CB8E4B665EDAD4E5F998944E4C37_72190CE: My life flashed before my eyes and then my heart stopped beating, forever.
Dialogue.F565F01042507BF27B3C01A430FB0A7E_861A10F: My sledge is at your service.
Dialogue.0EB1D3E34FC7D586D59058BCB5C7CA94_861A10F: Never get between a lady and her tools.
Dialogue.914DDEAD462B01973CB8BBA7A5A73AD4_97A9259: Nice job clearing out those husks.
Dialogue.BE6964824636CB7F7CD6CC98F38F53DB_97A9259: Nice work, Commander. Now everyone gets gifts!
Dialogue.1BD9EA4944E352237C1E61AB49A6D88F_0ADEFA4: No one is going to believe this.
Dialogue.31E3DD3645C5953668E787803224F9A2_AB3C42C: No, I mean... it's not even a hologram. It's just a room.
Dialogue.8EF5D26F4DDED59E96A0F0918A590581_FB122F8: No, I mean... look at THIS.
Dialogue.CCBDD8C84931F124289FC0AB2808712B_06FC410: Not that I'm in it for the awards.
Dialogue.8F7CDAE345FD58403D7191B55AFDD02C_47CFF90: Not to be overly prescriptive, but I suggest building bridges.
Dialogue.087A0F7D4BC9B06DDBD6518BCE1DD4AA_C2C5A2E: Now begone from my sight foul peasant!
Dialogue.C1B81DCB463F086D7812D78E28E1E56E_C2C5A2E: Now to the work of building my kingdom!
Dialogue.B0E04162435191623FDF6FA906A4E720_97A9259: Now we just need to live through the night!
Dialogue.D4A31E2E4D4E4C796A2F0B8B19619823_47CFF90: Now would be a perfect time to, perhaps, revive your teammates. Please?
Dialogue.760C0F904BD4912270D99BA4807158AF_47CFF90: Oh again. My apologies. You're wonderful, and your constant mistake-making is informative. And reliable.
Dialogue.4B637B37486D2B73C1A0288D952A2FF1_C2C5A2E: Oh! Place the logs. From this hardship my kingdom will rise once more.
Dialogue.AC9C1EC44C24ED445C8AB3ABE7DD25CF_C2C5A2E: Oh! That thing will smash the fort!
Dialogue.D5D23B054D5126F74AB900A5A839A80C_C2C5A2E: Oh! You are proposing a trade.
Dialogue.82539F1048C3F7695852A6AAFFBCE21F_861A10F: Oh, I don't like the feel of this room.
Dialogue.B9B980C94378915778822998FFB00F5C_97A9259: Oh, I love unauthorized versions. It's like, who gave you the authority?
Dialogue.7F3D612745F674822DB620A00683F512_97A9259: Oh, and I signed us up three-ish times, so expect multiple presents at once.
Dialogue.43E08C0640D7F15D8E8C4F868F90C16B_06FC410: Oh, no no no no no! We're out of time! We're all going to die!
Dialogue.151067C34900E057E5323786D46F9BB3_C2C5A2E: Oh, no. Just slip something dead in a rotten pile of leaves and deposit them under my throne.
Dialogue.007607CA44D43B7B7E30A49A0CC17008_861A10F: Oh, no. These wounds feel mortal
Dialogue.535FE9B3422A64235CA54CA372C68BB8_861A10F: Oh, no. They're walking our way.
Dialogue.EB9C507D4BAFBCCCF679C1AB6A17F6D5_72190CE: Oh, yeah. Ray, hit Alt-F7, please.
Dialogue.576CA8DB47C329FDFD7A96B7693B3B1D_06FC410: Oh. I guess that's not necessary. Wow.
Dialogue.37490FC74F7F1355354A2C94C7365485_C2C5A2E: Oh. I was practicing looking like I was listening, but not actually listening, it is the skill of many a great king.
Dialogue.5D16CE1343C42B8F57605EBEF7B5FE24_B222EAD: Okay, fine. I'll keep you safe.
Dialogue.A505C00143DFE7B2FE6650B02A63134D_72190CE: Okay. And I don't want to tell you how to do your job, but make sure they're facing the ocean.
Dialogue.E6D649784391937A7D245DBEC780E992_06FC410: Okay... I can't believe I'm suggesting this...
Dialogue.32C008AC442A174E0B18C3A82EBF585A_97A9259: On tonight's episode of Ghost Boss, we survive the night at a haunted hotel.
Dialogue.3E7C8FBB4EDC4993636996AD7CD5220F_47CFF90: Once a base falls, it won't receive additional supplies. So keep those bases standing!
Dialogue.352F364443CE66D5326FA29A54C7F78C_47CFF90: Ooh, well. That certainly sounds like tomorrow's problem to me.
Dialogue.98A06B8D495728F5C7D585B76D442F82_861A10F: Ooh. What's this? "The Unauthorized History of the Oakdirge Hollows Hotel."
Dialogue.BE683F3342DE7EB817916AA1BCDF3F35_861A10F: Oooh. Strange. I Just got chills.
Dialogue.167125CE406E550ED70BDDB3E02BF8C7_47CFF90: Or go all in for a high risk melee attack.
Dialogue.FA44AF4B40686C8140B5FE838EB17DB7_47CFF90: Or natural disasters getting along. Either way, this is not ideal.
Dialogue.AA41BAC8481C251152B394A3359B10AF_47CFF90: Our first base has just been compromised.
Dialogue.BDE8DF9C4B316623457046B8B10A7E34_06FC410: Our mission is to pry open a wild rift long enough for Carlos to escape.
Dialogue.797CDD424F7846D5A4B0C3A6FD2CE7FA_97A9259: Our mission is to survive the night.
Dialogue.A6C3D05A493475505E7303BA0A8B8F82_AB3C42C: Our set designer was really into backpacking. Maybe we'll find something at one of the campsites around here.
Dialogue.B62434734BE2183BE7850F89685961E5_C2C5A2E: Pah! A king rallies behind no one.
Dialogue.A6493F96432F43BD7154D4BD4DB5A8B0_47CFF90: Perhaps I should disable my comm.
Dialogue.23E36C7C4A9EF8217E9FCDBDE36F1880_47CFF90: Place sensors around the hotel campus.
Dialogue.46EA1F694B8E67344D157294E0B8177D_06FC410: Place the lasers on the locations marked on your map.
Dialogue.35AA7E034CD62DD0F222D3ADCFFC1B95_06FC410: Place the rift stabilization device on the rift.
Dialogue.E831CAF0412D6936704DC3BD7474948F_06FC410: Please, no one build it then steal it.
Dialogue.FDA69EF348B479587CB351AA9CBFDC36_97A9259: Present incoming. Check your map for details!
Dialogue.2D5F541B44FF24A093BEE590C32AEF44_B25AF7B: RETREAT! RETREAT! REVERSE COURSE! TURN HER ABOUT!
Dialogue.9B651C54407593EFFAB842BC7734BFA5_47CFF90: Ranged attacks still work, but if your team wants to risk an up-close fight, it might be worth it.
Dialogue.A657AD7D4AAC79540C783DA4BFB45717_47CFF90: Ranged weapons still work, so the choice is yours.
Dialogue.9B23FABD40CB381244A1F59FB315ABF1_06FC410: Remember, these rifts are mean. They will try to kill you.
Dialogue.000D5F3344AF6203810C7F87728DED5E_FB122F8: Search the zone for the X.
Dialogue.32160DBD4F9F4863AFAF828DEE575E22_06FC410: Search the zone for the perfect place to build your ship.
Dialogue.77A953554243363181C8C481AC2D4983_861A10F: Send that smasher back to cloud town.
Dialogue.68A9085342F83875773329A4F477D8F4_CC240C1: Should I be worried about spending the night here?
Dialogue.EAF92F68405831C2C0EF898A97ED6D5A_47CFF90: Should have read that one first. That's on me.
Dialogue.EC50946948B1D01911DC37907BA1346F_47CFF90: Sit tight. We are going to get your team out of there.
Dialogue.7408AE044D9DD85B30EAB1981F762197_C2C5A2E: Smashers and this fort don't mix.
Dialogue.95C8ADAA4499F118430359A38129C3EA_861A10F: So don't go chattering on about it.
Dialogue.CAE3EEE74802A247046C4292A49ED43C_47CFF90: So if you can, you may want to take the fight to the pillars themselves.
Dialogue.4CDACF624C1D718ACA7D8EB7F59B833F_47CFF90: So keep those bases standing and I'll keep the supplies flowing.
Dialogue.7652942B42DC7A4D2E9526A03A656EF4_47CFF90: So let's see what we're working with here.
Dialogue.7DBC5D03487AA7E7AF9189A8194BAAD0_06FC410: So long as the set is a box. Or a pyramid...
Dialogue.79DFEAA840F9163DF34884853308A648_FB122F8: So track down the anti-pirate munition stash, prepare defenses, and see what those cannons can do.
Dialogue.B24AB7EF43675F5A75D2DDBCD9B0E203_94F2B66: So we can destroy the rifts with BluGlo?
Dialogue.FD9BAD1A41A20D623B9ACEA633595835_06FC410: So, is this how you remember it?
Dialogue.EDFADE6A44E4A495D58ED490C236903D_97A9259: So, we need to protect our presents.
Dialogue.45554860436776018712FB851738074E_97A9259: So. Get ready for sky presents!
Dialogue.93625DB04ABFC44C98AD6683882722F4_47CFF90: So... don't touch the melted rock. It's hot.
Dialogue.84E32FA5442ABB13C05349AA7EFA31C9_AB3C42C: Some of the set... we'll need to rebuild.
Dialogue.3101E3804E48930F138F358DCA5C15A8_06FC410: Speaking of alarming things - we've got multiple rifts reported in the area,
Dialogue.F9C64C134696A7082F4CFE9C9BED3416_72190CE: Speaking of, I noticed you didn't RSVP to my funeral.
Dialogue.52161A0C4081D70AC0A9CCA45B64F4A8_B222EAD: Speaking of, do you want to hang out here forever and ever and ever?
Dialogue.17723FE74BE4BE28B52F80B299F53C04_06FC410: Take a look around. You've earned a break.
Dialogue.F116BF044A86568F31CD409443D40940_47CFF90: Take a moment. You've earned it. But, heh heh... just a moment.
Dialogue.F7370E7E49D8D544F6E1C1815039026F_47CFF90: Take out the bosses to end the wave!
Dialogue.0083C68046A67F20A2F724A6E10149A0_97A9259: Take out the creepers and just maybe we'll make it to dawn.
Dialogue.B050282E4066327812F5308E7DC46F56_47CFF90: Take out the pillars to end the wave!
Dialogue.8587B55649C3F724A38D22961B86502C_06FC410: Thank you for bringing him home.
Dialogue.D70D3E9B40ACB4A5F9B7F3A3964E1396_72190CE: Thank you for supporting my family in this very trying time.
Dialogue.107F6D024C895B65ADF1E5AD03FE42C8_0ADEFA4: Thanks again for your help, see you soon.
Dialogue.BF83B7BE48CE37EF2DB886939687CE85_06FC410: That breaks my brain and my heart.
Dialogue.F3DA661E4890CCD96B7021BF18B39717_06FC410: That didn't make sense. That's never made sense. Why did I try it?
Dialogue.55B886E94B12349632912399F88A7D02_FB122F8: That looks like an X to me.
Dialogue.77280DAB45FBCC33FD8348819B7E4C0E_06FC410: That turned the once thriving Gravestone into an aptly named ghost town.
Dialogue.C9CF6A3F494C79D51D63FD8BF60CCE41_C2C5A2E: That was an agreement made in a time of peace.
Dialogue.F151BFCC42BBF9739E1DC68A0D321491_72190CE: That's how you welcome a fallen friend?
Dialogue.7E11AE764E12A8A006134CB1AFAFE8BE_06FC410: That's it! I'm turning you off!
Dialogue.3D8EC3FB430F929992DF12AD06072C6E_06FC410: That's what I was afraid of...
Dialogue.8506DB3E42E2B05F0F60F1AB2A9C1BAB_47CFF90: The Homebase extraction team is headed your way!
Dialogue.3C828EDE4FD41C994D5339B5648ABEF1_FB122F8: The X marks the spot where the anti-pirate munitions are stashed.
Dialogue.F04BC1F84E03C8C776629AA11940FA88_47CFF90: The cavern, the depot, the volcano and the mine.
Dialogue.560AF6F04A427C4EC4C8EFA058FE45D7_C2C5A2E: The doll speaks of it often, but I do not wish to see it at this late hour.
Dialogue.8FF4E5BF411E01FF3041E1AD46D411FD_47CFF90: The extraction team has completed their snack stop and is on their way!
Dialogue.48812D054CAC946051B1CFB6AB48078F_47CFF90: The extraction team has dislodged themselves from a fallen tree and is en route.
Dialogue.ECDD522B40C7AE57EE70CB82F1E6C359_97A9259: The husks got to the present drop! Its too late.
Dialogue.AF73ADE849241E1D51B80E9A5902DDD7_06FC410: The intergalactic exchange planet back alley.
Dialogue.3D8A0BCF478DDE7D2752A795405D4C58_C2C5A2E: The kingdom of exits 7b through 7c will quake in awe at the sight of such a log.
Dialogue.CA8A925741318AC382F21C8025D7D51E_FB122F8: The last time we had a pirate raid, I prepared a stash of anti-pirate munitions.
Dialogue.0E8CCB8A4304905AB2EDAB910FAB0C43_06FC410: The legendary gunslinger, Blackboot Ayers, is gone!
Dialogue.2A0F68EC479EFF180E69308B123E7DC4_47CFF90: The light beams should guide you to the critical objectives.
Dialogue.80B7839A4A567BCA311B5CB737A291A0_47CFF90: The mining expedition set up four bases before the storm hit.
Dialogue.69D2C1DC48CEA56E60AD8D996419EF96_06FC410: The more lasers you have active, the faster we'll get this done.
Dialogue.C6052A29454D46EC140A81A6BDA85D98_47CFF90: The pillars are vulnerable to melee attacks!
Dialogue.A35390B340D8C8BA21081D93DD5FBC6D_47CFF90: The pillars take more damage from melee weapons... but be careful out there.
Dialogue.B47D78B74FEE5825AD5901A25BCFBCC4_06FC410: The plans should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue.395D17F542EB20047B6EFCB5BD75C75E_97A9259: The present drop didn't make it.
Dialogue.EE8172BA436ED1584407588ACF85CF03_97A9259: The present drop is taking heavy damage!
Dialogue.648396DA46408963F309438CC4DAE2AC_97A9259: The present is down. Build those defenses!
Dialogue.A090189B45F48470AB942DA8EB9850B9_47CFF90: The rescue team has turned the map right-side up, and are headed your way.
Dialogue.FF17CC714A82CD528ED6E4979A3E36D8_06FC410: The rifts kill anything that gets too close.
Dialogue.88EBB0904D870E453040A285FF7B9587_47CFF90: The second base is down. Only one left.
Dialogue.E34142834A20575D6B6C2C93B887B123_97A9259: The sensors are ready to sense!
Dialogue.000541FB466408B2BB710B9873578AB1_97A9259: The sensors won't work with takers around!
Dialogue.E6F1E13F45DF6BB591861E8E76868090_47CFF90: The storm has a new target!
Dialogue.89B3057340639E13025C9F827FAC56E5_47CFF90: The storm has taken over the volcano!
Dialogue.D4C28160419B2FABAC7E82A09E0F0E6F_47CFF90: The storm is attacking the volcano base!
Dialogue.54ADC8F44D7E7C0FAA0E89883FED8D4E_47CFF90: The storm is attacking the volcano!
Dialogue.80AC21DC4C107D4C81A2ED9CE636D97E_47CFF90: The storm is attacking the volcano?
Dialogue.6AD9840A44EB91157DBCB5A3BB42EC6F_47CFF90: The storm is targeting the cavern!
Dialogue.6737A2E247BA5B3674332CBE4E2D16B6_47CFF90: The storm is targeting the depot!
Dialogue.0FA8F26941253CED721B2F9FC41F3BA0_47CFF90: The storm is targeting the mine!
Dialogue.C74007BD4CFA26A2317BDA98D8C6DE8A_47CFF90: The time between husk waves is decreasing.
Dialogue.5ACE5B38425DEA73A757298EB51D3061_47CFF90: The wave won't end until those pillars are destroyed!
Dialogue.3FFE83FF429C0C3B1AC7FB836AFE5B72_47CFF90: The waves are coming faster now! Good luck!
Dialogue.0AD75FA7415B50F0BC4FD99CBC6E0926_861A10F: There are enough flavors of nightmare to go around. We don't need to add our own.
Dialogue.594C8BC5475182847F27DA8E78C9A796_B222EAD: They can only sort of sense me.
Dialogue.27355DBB47B178749FE41DAC8B4021A4_C2C5A2E: This fort can't hold back smashers!
Dialogue.46B87712489B77D4B5E494AAEE67DCC1_06FC410: This here town weren't big enough for both of us.
Dialogue.52640CE54CDB0E3EF89D08AC67AA0EE7_47CFF90: This is a genuine "floor is lava" situation.
Dialogue.9CD8C1894B505F2643333AB72FCB7CAC_47CFF90: This is a tough fight, but you're my very best team.
Dialogue.0CEBCF464B014D49397CB9B3AB9DC936_47CFF90: This is all resting on you now.
Dialogue.BDFA83E84AD8F84F91E6E98B4C9C5C26_B222EAD: This is an inescapably evil place, Lok.
Dialogue.A4DE4A4A4EB85C20C5611E809F8E1DE9_B222EAD: This is the Door to Darkness.
Dialogue.56FB0F004396003465ACD089273FAA80_06FC410: This may or may not be a sign that this is a terrible idea.
Dialogue.00A391E84C32DBCBA55EC583EDAF12AE_FB122F8: This mission will give us a chance to test out our new Cannon Aided Defense.
Dialogue.684045784897F8289EF8C795CB6ADC1D_47CFF90: This wave of husks seems to be coming from those strange pillars.
Dialogue.4D6C34764A13317BFB3FBAB16F4EC52B_C2C5A2E: Those flingers are going to start flinging!
Dialogue.E0081618445218D95B9EBEB1C9280D8C_861A10F: Time to get my hands dirty!
Dialogue.6AB29C2A497A0A8FCE1CB3909C4107D9_B222EAD: Two hundred and fifty-six... counting me.
Dialogue.5725E2904A31DC29295E568DBF238AD6_B222EAD: UNLESS ONE OF YOU WALKS OVER MY GRAVE!
Dialogue.69452E9044E24C6FABF7198420F749EB_06FC410: Ugh, fine. This is my ship.
Dialogue.98C685E04CA6A4513129D59B61DEF412_C2C5A2E: Ugh. I no longer want this one. It is crying.
Dialogue.477623314766BF0BA3F662BD8E1308F9_0ADEFA4: Uh, hi! I need a small favor!
Dialogue.F70F03CC412DCE31DCCF2DA3E9E7F983_47CFF90: Unless you revive your teammates. Which I highly recommend.
Dialogue.CFFA628C4D3FF40A69B7BB85E2004A78_C2C5A2E: Very well. I shall release you, but I must insist you continue to pay the tax.
Dialogue.5AA339CA47921A337900BA9E4E8DE4D6_06FC410: Wait. I've got another location? That must be an error.
Dialogue.981EBA9244ADF78AA4CA51852EB34AE9_06FC410: Wait... did you know how to do that this whole time?
Dialogue.DCBB27074927385463E8BEAB3C038A55_C2C5A2E: Want more shooting? Need more ammo.
Dialogue.C68DE5C04122A31FEF6AF6AC42F0669A_861A10F: Was that a flock or a gaggle?
Dialogue.DAE4D54644540EDF03A17BAFD5DD0031_97A9259: Way to go! More husks down.
Dialogue.17755D2A40327BBB9B82EEB04E97DB66_97A9259: We didn't eliminate enough husks. Better luck next time
Dialogue.E9DADB2D4342E34E4644E3A4D1F7B0CF_06FC410: We find ourselves on a trajectory to adventure.
Dialogue.1838ED724801DD8C94AD5D98FC54BB83_47CFF90: We have a break in the action!
Dialogue.AEB294034DBDDA65C92DCEB04E7456CC_47CFF90: We have a break in the storm.
Dialogue.F530E90E434149D1103B6E9F2521970C_47CFF90: We have a moment to breathe between husks.
Dialogue.B7AAA27C4BA32DA412AC77A9FB535389_C2C5A2E: We have a troll here. Ugh, vermin!
Dialogue.F9585A5C4EBAE9CAC751178E8CF67D2D_47CFF90: We have an update from our chief meteorologist...
Dialogue.02537D1A4859E6AA5BC577A6E6540359_47CFF90: We have sensors I found in a box labeled "Ghost Sensors, Question Mark."
Dialogue.A427316A4CB983EC51905EB48527376E_06FC410: We have to clear out all husks before starting.
Dialogue.44F48D4A45A60F4C2AE281A9E99FF4BF_06FC410: We might need some building plans.
Dialogue.92E3AF84469356FE9DF51F8ED9E6D603_0ADEFA4: We need more people like you.
Dialogue.4E29415646A7E651E711FCBFDC711E7E_06FC410: We need to build the hologram room!
Dialogue.A2F369DE4CD9DA56F99758B44F5DC23D_06FC410: We need to power the device.
Dialogue.C42CBDDF450933132CCBF88FAD6C39B9_47CFF90: We need to recover everyone we can before the break in the storm closes.
Dialogue.F584D3B449496F53DF8E5FAC847777AA_97A9259: We should try to protect all the presents.
Dialogue.D0F96DC0455F28B875B10386E22CAB8A_06FC410: We'll have to restock and try again.
Dialogue.40EAB0F24833EF13E6DB7BB42C5DED04_861A10F: We'll leave you to say your goodbyes now.
Dialogue.472CAB7C4429112AF1ED0FAE70B68997_AB3C42C: We'll need to rebuild before we even start rehearsals.
Dialogue.37BA5D774EDD050844978596842F1256_47CFF90: We're about to embark on a seven-day, six-night journey into terror.
Dialogue.0B55606343467B90D3C5579CF348A1FB_47CFF90: We're back in business! Let's get back to the mission.
Dialogue.7AFD82F540D9B68AEECCAE8C801BDF51_97A9259: We're detecting a big wave incoming! Get ready!
Dialogue.291DA556411811B004217FA33E6DAE7E_97A9259: We're good on the creepy imaginary friend updates for the moment.
Dialogue.29195A18426C529E9B728CBA8B2A8DA5_AB3C42C: We're missing a lot of the set.
Dialogue.009BDFDE4D7ACE85E54C2BABBCE145FA_47CFF90: We're taking heavy damage and need assistance.
Dialogue.81F0152141FAC76B7DC0EABC84FB8AC7_47CFF90: We've been training for this our entire lives, people.
Dialogue.E81DA60E44DC610FE09EBA9FFAD28379_FB122F8: We've brought in some cannons to help the fight along.
Dialogue.1D563C1145954B6CE1A6BD8E0677DDB4_97A9259: We've done it! I told you there was nothing to be scared about.
Dialogue.F53587824114EB313046A9901A2C28C9_06FC410: We've got a bonus in play.
Dialogue.F805F9CC42B84D19D7B4B98CCF5A1096_47CFF90: We've got a break in the action!
Dialogue.C3786E344470E67C489AA8B8BC63A636_47CFF90: We've got a break, heal up and repair what you can.
Dialogue.A203A0274F4D3837D5E2E581BCFDA5B5_47CFF90: We've got a mini-boss wave headed our way!
Dialogue.FB1872B74F109378361EB9A5BE258849_06FC410: We've got him in our sights!
Dialogue.FA3514E5405B55154120388FFFBBAEFD_97A9259: We've got husks inbound... I assume.
Dialogue.166CB12744083942684ABFB1E7F05A33_97A9259: Welcome to Ghost Boss: Survive the Night Edition.
Dialogue.21A84822489C8851E6B9FA98F90E077D_06FC410: What are you guys up to?
Dialogue.5E31881141BD32C9C72F3AA1165BF038_06FC410: Where some of the galaxy's grittiest grifters meet to cut their cutthroat deals.
Dialogue.882CB88B4E31EDBD41AC218BFA3E0011_06FC410: Which I do not know how to do.
Dialogue.1188DBDA41822D9D682740BBB455F1EA_47CFF90: Which means I need to add yet another entry to our disaster preparedness guide.
Dialogue.3C19359E4F176FC89511E08669197499_47CFF90: While I do value a clear reporting structure, I am getting sick of all of these Bosses!
Dialogue.DB020E354A97C37276AF5AA407845DE2_861A10F: Why did it have to be a flinger?
Dialogue.BC9553604B6FEF15DB0EB09E1ACB838C_06FC410: Why don't you investigate the rift.
Dialogue.1301ECDD46A62A12FE43D78A4119775D_C2C5A2E: Will you lay down your life so I may once again claim the musty throne of my fetid kingdom?
Dialogue.6B0769F7496518CFB999F798F50FFF33_CC240C1: Willow says it's two hundred and fifty-six guests!
Dialogue.B115626449BD27BBB70A4ABAE5728047_CC240C1: Willow says this is the door to the darkness.
Dialogue.0A90EC634D15D96731A3A7832B2E2554_CC240C1: Yeah, I was gonna ask about that.
Dialogue.9C8B91104A2EB294D283DF834278AFB2_B222EAD: Yeah, Lok. I mean, look at me.
Dialogue.AE74F09D44185425CE5460A743871A00_72190CE: Yeah, you know, like "Oh god, it's Blakebeard! Why would this happen? I don't want to die!"
Dialogue.FB4C6BBC4137BEF97103B2A225170633_C2C5A2E: Yes, quite. I SAID BE GONE!
Dialogue.4012EB8748223BC6FEA849BADE1D2A34_861A10F: You can go harvest if you need more resources.
Dialogue.D676D7E543257B81B6B95B89993E55AC_B222EAD: You can walk over my grave all day long. I don't care.
Dialogue.8F7D2B1C4746F121D94078BE6A8AC256_EAAE146: You don't build a pirate ship.
Dialogue.4C260D75426FBE055C83DA972457441A_0ADEFA4: You have to help me get out of here!
Dialogue.14F1A11141CB8374E544048E2C6CA79B_47CFF90: You have, uh... some amount of time to setup before first wave. Good luck, Commander.
Dialogue.47049A3F4C68C0AEF265068D93697487_97A9259: You just might be ghost boss material yourself.
Dialogue.AB88F2F24FB68CEE08FE8898AABB4A8F_97A9259: You know I'm callin' that number.
Dialogue.25EA3D5548FDF54FAD8893B924A5D4E7_861A10F: You know we're gonna win, yeah?
Dialogue.9CE3454A41720114FA2406B99D80A9FE_06FC410: You know, people used to say Dr. Vinderman was arrogant.
Dialogue.5A26422C4E932009A85FAA9F0953E0D8_861A10F: You look like you could use this.
Dialogue.1FBAC2374F8CB59C2E8DDB940D70CAA4_47CFF90: You may have noticed the burning rivers of molten rock crisscrossing the map.
Dialogue.775FAC1142F56DB4C98A7E96F5861054_FB122F8: You might want to take a look at this.
Dialogue.C61C161D4D294F6D5843C9A9FF180078_FB122F8: You needed our help so you attacked us?
Dialogue.E115F54B4FFE8AC1312EE188A3923408_06FC410: You only have 1 day until I pull you out!  Finish up what you can!
Dialogue.86AFD8544FD5FD29375BB9936E0F99F2_06FC410: You will take some damage when you place the rift stabilization device.
Dialogue.DEB6CA7D490EE62A8550A68266DF524F_47CFF90: You will take the leap, and become pirates.
Dialogue.036A2E134A12600A9934A58D2FDD6A7E_47CFF90: You won't be able to harvest this far out in the storm, so use your materials wisely...
Dialogue.D952FBEF40FF655539931F82C6A2A01F_47CFF90: You'll need to be able to move quickly to defend all three bases.
Dialogue.F10F9CE64EBAC6E56503BFB0D26E3270_47CFF90: You'll need to destroy the pillars to end the wave.
Dialogue.982E02924997E44720BE68BAD8D6BE09_47CFF90: You're already a hero in my eyes, but...heh heh, if you're up for another round...
Dialogue.D0F561DC48ED9432E55F8B9D1361E9C2_47CFF90: You're doing great, keep it up!
Dialogue.DA0B87BF4E1F3D1B42F7359B22A50D32_47CFF90: You're doing great, keep it up!
Dialogue.51EB1BB1459D6413D6D55F9F7A0B4E9D_97A9259: You're on a roll! Keep it up. New bonus objective on the way.
Dialogue.2F1A42A548D88330BCB844BBAF6414FA_97A9259: You're running out of time! Take out more husks or we fail the... episode.
Dialogue.BDB64E8E4086B2DA1A9249900FFC349C_47CFF90: You're the only one left! Be careful!
Dialogue.792CAFBB4F9B67AF88B53486FC0F7248_47CFF90: You're too far out to harvest, but we'll keep you supplied.
Dialogue.6470B2254DD0A85D95353C917D14C3DC_97A9259: You've got a bonus objective! Protect the next package
Dialogue.E621783B431F2A7455A5FA9F1619F76C_47CFF90: You've got a lot of ground to cover. Don't forget to build bridges.
Dialogue.D4D97D164B5DB15214510CB79DCFDECE_97A9259: You've got the holiday spirit, huh? Those gifts are safe.
Dialogue.8A2760724F0F6EB410E84C86EF892E8F_47CFF90: You've got time to heal up!
Dialogue.6541E7BE48C18B8E5AC2B5ACF2A80A6F_861A10F: You. Big guy. Respect the architecture.
Dialogue.8C7B1ABC4902F4E53B4C6396B1FFE629_C2C5A2E: Your bountiful pit of roiling maggots?!
Dialogue.1E2691B044B6F3DFD44F98A42544F047_C2C5A2E: Your corridor of summer ripened, fecund garbage?
Dialogue.F9E3722149560F93F35932839854F4CD_B222EAD: Your friends who left you without a buddy after "buddy up" was declared?
Dialogue.C0DC4D3D44C9EF84F0CBFAA4FED0D4AA_C2C5A2E: Your kindness shall not be forgotten, King Riggs.
Dialogue.2082532F4BC3862E7B5307964848E4D6_C2C5A2E: Your softest logs from the darkest dankest rankest murk holes in your most desolate forest.
Dialogue.E0B19CEA4A51EA27801004A8BFE61343_72190CE: Your team's doing great against the husks.
Dialogue.CDC2F67144EF4D242109839E88BBD076_06FC410: and according to Lars' data, if those rifts remain active our storm shield will be overrun in...
